"GBIF produces https://www.gbif.org/composition/3NZQV4dMHw154WEwu4TqDw/guides-"
"and-documentation#_gbif-digital-guides[digital guides^] on a range of topics "
"relating to biodiversity informatics and open biodiversity data to support "
"the community of practice."
msgstr ""

#. type: Title ===
#: en/intro-to-gbif/modules/ROOT/pages/data-access.adoc:100
